skill-creator-advance
=====================

Upstream chain
--------------

This skill is adapted from a chain of MIT-licensed upstream projects:

1. Anthropic `skill-creator` — the earliest upstream.
   https://github.com/anthropics/skills/tree/main/skills/skill-creator
   License: MIT. Contributes the overall eval-loop concept + file naming
   for bundled agents (grader, comparator, analyzer) and bundled scripts
   (aggregate_benchmark, run_eval, run_loop, improve_description,
   package_skill, quick_validate, generate_report, utils).

2. AllanYiin (尹相志) `skill-creator-advanced` — direct upstream.
   https://github.com/AllanYiin/Amon
   Path: src/amon/resources/skills/skill-creator-advanced/
   License: MIT. Copyright (c) 2026 AllanYiin.
   Announcement (Chinese): https://www.facebook.com/allanyiin/posts/26778210211773012/
   Allan's own reference files explicitly acknowledge the Anthropic
   upstream (e.g., references/eval-workflow.md and references/eval-schemas.md
   state "upstream skill-creator" as source for the eval loop and field
   designs).

3. kouko monkey-skills — this distribution.
   https://github.com/kouko/monkey-skills
   Path: dev-workflow/skills/skill-creator-advance/
   License: MIT. Copyright (c) 2026 kouko.

Modifications in this distribution (kouko)
------------------------------------------

See dev-workflow/CHANGELOG.md for the full per-version modification list.
High-level summary (v1.0.0):

- monkey-skills ecosystem integration guidance
- Description best practices (negative triggers, multilingual keywords)
- Eval flow tiering (quick path vs full path)
- Existing skill improvement workflow
- Slash command creation guidance
- Self-assessment pass (auto-fix obvious defects before human review)
- Auto-regression detection across iterations
- Eval results presented inline + markdown report (removed browser viewer
  dependency)
- Token-based budget (~6,000 tokens) instead of line-based (500 lines)
- Platform adaptations extracted to reference file (optional, load on demand)

v1.0.1 (license compliance fix): added LICENSE and NOTICE files to
correctly attribute the upstream chain; previous CHANGELOG text
incorrectly claimed direct Anthropic upstream when the actual direct
upstream was AllanYiin/Amon skill-creator-advanced.

